      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade example that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, protected from the elements since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, showroom luster with a professional-grade ceramic coating and absolutely zero stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in a factory-fresh state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear or aging, and the interior retains its original new-car scent. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule exclusively at authorized service centers. Every electronic component, switch, and luxury feature functions perfectly. This sale includes all original keys, the complete set of owner\u2019s manuals, and a comprehensive binder of service documentation. For the discerning buyer seeking a turn-key masterpiece that looks and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor, this vehicle is unparalleled.",
